should be secretly bringing
in Pollen Orb ingredients.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0003

A Superbian woman stands out
around here, you see.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0004
rows.name:
The cargo was transported near
the ruins of the main
gate of Old Gelgemos.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0005
rows.name:
Seems like the woman
is making something there.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0007
rows.name:
Who knows[ML:Dash ] I wonder?
I haven't grasped
what exactly she is making.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0008
rows.name:
I see[ML:Dash ]
Thanks for the info.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0009
rows.name:
If it's the ruins of the main
gate of Old Gelgemos, it's
closest to go from the Genbu Drifts.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0010
rows.name:
That's right.
Even so, we've finally
caught Harghal's tail.

rows.label: qst200220_msg0011
rows.name:
Yeah!
Finally, we'll meet Harghal
face-to-face!! Let's get fired up!!
